{"name":"A-HA!","type":"move","img":"icons/creatures/unholy/demons-horned-glowing-pink.webp","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you <strong>attempt to prove the Fiend or a Shadow are lying or wrong</strong>, call it out and roll +Hope.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"fiend","rollFormula":"2d6 + @attributesTop.hope.value","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":"<p>You catch it by surprise and reveal a weakness. The Fiend retreats/the Shadow crumbles. -1 Fear.</p>"},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial Success","value":"<p>It doubles down and tries to talk itself out of the predicament. It promises to return to you and make you sorry but leaves you alone for now.</p>"},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":"<p>It laughs at you and explains how your mind cannot comprehend its workings. +1XP.</p>"}},"playbook":"","rollType":"formula","rollMod":null,"choices":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zqb0MpDkOYkFKPTb":3},"flags":{},"_id":"vSsvYvzdGzGkVjdW"}
{"name":"Face Off","type":"move","img":"icons/magic/death/skull-horned-worn-fire-blue.webp","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you <strong>are confronted by the Fiend</strong>, roll -Fear.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"fiend","rollFormula":"2d6 - @attributesTop.fear.value","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":"<p>It makes a threat and a future promise. +1 Fear and +1XP.</p>"},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial Success","value":"<p>It will offer you something you want in exchange for (choose one):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Private and potentially harmful information on another player.</li>\n<li>Acceptance of a private mission or sabotage.</li>\n<li>Destruction of a sentimental item.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Rejecting the offer gives +1 Fear.</p>"},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":"<p>Your resolve is strong. While it attempts to manipulate or frighten you, you stick up for yourself and the Fiend retreats. +1 Hope.</p>"}},"playbook":"","rollType":"formula","rollMod":0,"choices":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zqb0MpDkOYkFKPTb":3},"flags":{},"_id":"Gwmf5ca2PsgLda1q"}
{"name":"Find a Clue","type":"move","img":"icons/sundries/books/book-face-blue.webp","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you find or infer evidence of the Fiend&rsquo;s recent presence or influence, tell the others up to 3 rumors about the Fiend that scare you. Then, roll +Rumors.</p>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"fiend","rollFormula":"","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"key":"data.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Complications...","value":"<p>All of your rumors are true. You feel a chill up your spine and the presence of the Fiend but you don&rsquo;t see it. +1 Fear and +1XP.</p>"},"partial":{"key":"data.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial Success","value":"<p>Choose one of your rumors to be based in truth but worse than you thought. An agent or omen of the Fiend presents itself to the group in an attempt to deter you.</p>"},"success":{"key":"data.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":"<p>Choose one of your rumors to be true and another to be false. The shadowy presence or evidence dissipates.</p>"}},"playbook":"","rollType":"ask","rollMod":0,"choices":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zqb0MpDkOYkFKPTb":3},"flags":{},"_id":"GkJ6AJ3CyqlzWuY1"}
